        "overview-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Set on one of Boston's most storied streets, this four-story townhouse balances period craftsmanship with considered modern updates. Original hardwoods, three working fireplaces, and a private south-facing garden are paired with a renovated chef's kitchen, updated mechanical systems, and a finished lower level.</p>",
